'''Veeone''' was [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade's]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] [[Droid/Legends|droid]] that she had on ''[[Jade's Fire]]''. She once referred to it as '''Slips'''. It spoke in a twittering chirp and was overly protective of the [[Starship/Legends|ship]].

